// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2312 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: b5f98ca1-0e0d-58ed-906d-15e1a056151d

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
